MODULE m_matrixRxR


! ----------------------------------------------------------------------
! MODULE: m_matrixRxR
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------
! Purpose:
!  Module for calling the following subroutines 
! 
! Subroutines contained within the module:
! - matrixRxR
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------
! Author :	Dr. Thomas Papanikolaou
!			Cooperative Research Centre for Spatial Information, Australia
! Created:	5 March 2018
